{"tid":725850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大學生自發開專頁「睇政」　籲關注政治犯　「現在更不應灰心」","createTime":"2018-07-02T02:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T02:55:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"81c906f7b5cd1482a22e4be13926a06aa58b5cda","tid":725850,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T02:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/watchpoli71cms-05_wags6_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fwatchpoli71cms-05_wags6_1200x0.png&h=5bd68ddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文大學政治及行政學系十多名學生，在一年前自發開facebook專頁「睇政」，希望透過拍片和懶人包，向更多年輕人解釋政治社會議題，例如以黃子華炒飛現象講述社會正義，以中大掛港獨旗論言論自由，及將推出有關土地大辯論的選項解釋等。<br />\n<br />\n成員Charlotte指，過去一年很多令人灰心的事情，如梁天琦等年輕人被判刑，但很多人或因香港紛亂的議題而少了人談。希望今次以啡色囚衣加上寫著118名被捕人士的紙牌，再引起關注。<br />\n<br />\n他指，現時政治環境差，難以靠一己之力去抗衡，七一具象徵意義讓港人發聲，故走出來很重要，「我們一開始就願意行出來的人，現在更不應灰心，繼續出來發聲。」<br />\n<br />\n他們有成員穿上啡色衣服，掛上「政治犯」字句，手持因政治運動入獄人士名單，希望市民關注政治犯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BC%E9%96%8B%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81-%E7%9D%87%E6%94%BF-%E7%B1%B2%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%8A%AF-%E7%8F%BE%E5%9C%A8%E6%9B%B4%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E7%81%B0%E5%BF%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581-%25E7%259D%2587%25E6%2594%25BF-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%258A%25AF-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%259B%25B4%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%2581%25B0%25E5%25BF%2583%2F&d=fyCun59eG1Q4uXOCRK3Ijm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1c21ac78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581-%25E7%259D%2587%25E6%2594%25BF-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%258A%25AF-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%259B%25B4%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2587%2589%25E7%2581%25B0%25E5%25BF%2583%2F&h=f41e2699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%83%E4%B8%80%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%87%AA%E7%99%BC%E9%96%8B%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81-%E7%9D%87%E6%94%BF-%E7%B1%B2%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%8A%AF-%E7%8F%BE%E5%9C%A8%E6%9B%B4%E4%B8%8D%E6%87%89%E7%81%B0%E5%BF%83/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/seeingpolitics/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fseeingpolitics%2F&d=fyCun59eG1Q4uXOCRK3Ijm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=06671a1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/seeingpolitics/</a>"}]}